hopobject.body: Languages lumarx hair removal device ebay Very strange that some unknown number of Native Americans supposedly are offended by the name “Redskins” while the Seminole tribe of Florida not only allows FSU to use the name “Seminoles” for its sports teams but also allows FSU to use caricatures of Native Americans (Chief Osceola, Sammy Seminole, et al) to sell tickets, tee shirts, hats, and various other products. Of course the Seminole tribe of Florida gets paid to do those things. Which suggests to me that Native Americans have been very well integrated into American society in at least one respect – money trumps principles every time.
